description:
UNIVERSE! - The Periodical of Cosmic Wonders is a DRM-free and pay-what-you-want digital comic written and illustrated by Albert Monteys and the second ongoing digital comic to be released by PanelSyndicate.com (The Private Eye). The first and second issues are available in English, Spanish, and Catalan.

As the title suggests and according to the author's afterword in the first issue, "UNIVERSE! will be a series of self-contained sci-fi tales that will be related to each other more or less directly."
name: UNIVERSE!
